1
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:11,560
Bitch,

2
00:00:11,560 --> 00:00:14,000
did you drug us yesterday?

3
00:00:18,030 --> 00:00:19,060
What kind of drug are you talking about, Madam?

4
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:20,060
I don't understand.

5
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:21,460
You still want to deny it?

6
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,400
The aphrodisiac was clearly in your tea cup.

7
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,560
How did it end up in Yingying's and my health soup?

8
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,700
It must be you.

9
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:30,360
Are you blaming me

10
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:32,560
for not suffering in silence?

11
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,330
Bitch!

12
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:36,530
If it weren't for the sake of our past friendship

13
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:38,130
that I bought your family out,

14
00:00:38,130 --> 00:00:40,000
you would be in a brothel by now.

15
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:40,830
You don't repay my kindness

16
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:41,960
with your life.

17
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:44,360
Instead, you dared to drug me and my mother.

18
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:46,060
When you entered the palace at the age of ten,

19
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:47,300
you broke a glazed cup.

20
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:50,030
You said your father would beat you to death if he knew.

21
00:00:50,030 --> 00:00:52,160
I was the one who took the blame for you.

22
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:54,600
At the spring banquet when you were fourteen,

23
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,300
you were jealous of my first place,

24
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:58,360
and put dirty things in my sachet.

25
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,200
I found out.

26
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,200
You knelt before me and begged me,

27
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,100
and I forgave you.

28
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,630
At my coming-of-age ceremony when I was sixteen,

29
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:04,760
at the Spring Festival when I was seventeen,

30
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,730
and at the Lantern Festival when I was eighteen...

31
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:07,530
Wei Yingying,

32
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:08,660
I have saved you,

33
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:10,600
helped you, and forgiven you so many times.

34
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:12,060
After you bought me,

35
00:01:12,230 --> 00:01:14,400
you took me to nineteen banquets of all sizes.

36
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,860
Every time, you would

37
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,500
do your best to humiliate me in front of everyone.

38
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:18,300
Wei Yingying,

39
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:21,200
did you buy me for the sake of our past friendship,

40
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,300
or just to humiliate me

41
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:23,760
and trample me into the mud?

42
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,400
We both know the answer.

43
00:01:25,730 --> 00:01:26,800
I just hate you,

44
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,600
Shen Lvyi.

45
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:30,330
I hate your always-so-arrogant look the most.

46
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,200
Madam, Second Miss, congratulations!

47
00:01:34,229 --> 00:01:36,300
The people from the General Weibei's Mansion have come to present betrothal gifts.

48
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:38,130
The gifts are piled up at the gate.

49
00:01:38,130 --> 00:01:40,060
There is no end in sight.

50
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:41,259
What?

51
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:43,560
I thought he had fallen out with our family.

52
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,530
It seems Lu Jingxing still dares not disobey the imperial order,

53
00:01:45,530 --> 00:01:48,530
nor is he willing to give up the power of our Wei family.

54
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:51,060
Shen Lvyi, do you see?

55
00:01:51,259 --> 00:01:54,229
The man you want to rely on has come to marry me.

56
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,660
I will be the wife of General Weibei.

57
00:01:58,259 --> 00:01:59,160
Shen Lvyi,

58
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,730
you'll never catch up with me in this life.

59
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,300
The door of this storehouse is too solid.

60
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:25,630
If it weren't for the chance of presenting betrothal gifts,

61
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,660
it would be harder than climbing to heaven

62
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:28,100
for us to get in.

63
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,460
An ordinary storehouse

64
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:33,130
doesn't need such tight security

65
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:34,230
and solid doors.

66
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:36,400
The posthumous edict we are looking for must be inside.

67
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,060
Let's go.

68
00:02:47,130 --> 00:02:48,100
Not here.

69
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:49,660
I didn't find it either.

70
00:02:56,530 --> 00:02:59,400
The storehouse is full of calligraphy and paintings by famous masters of the Tang and Song Dynasties.

71
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,600
The author of this painting is unknown.

72
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:03,200
The brushwork is vulgar.

73
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,930
It doesn't deserve to be hung here at all.

74
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:06,060
Something is wrong.

75
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,830
Found it.

76
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:14,660
Oh no.

77
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:16,829
Who's there?

78
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,230
We can't alert the enemy.

79
00:03:20,230 --> 00:03:22,100
Split up. You guys go out first.

80
00:03:28,329 --> 00:03:28,900
Stop right there.

81
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:29,900
You can't escape.

82
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:43,860
Why are you here?

83
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:46,500
Weren't you presenting betrothal gifts up front?

84
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,960
What's the fun in that?

85
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,530
I'm here to keep my lady company, of course.

86
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,530
Stealing is much more interesting.

87
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,960
I am looking for something.

88
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:57,230
But the mechanism is too intricate.

89
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:57,730
I can't unlock it,

90
00:03:57,730 --> 00:03:58,960
and they noticed me.

91
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,760
Help me.

92
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:03,730
Okay.

93
00:04:03,730 --> 00:04:05,430
I'll kill them right now,

94
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,700
and smash the mechanism for you.

95
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:08,560
No.

96
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,860
They are innocent.

97
00:04:10,230 --> 00:04:11,930
Besides, we can't cause trouble now

98
00:04:11,930 --> 00:04:13,060
and alert the enemy.

99
00:04:13,530 --> 00:04:15,260
Then there's only one way left.

100
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:16,899
What is it?

101
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:24,760
Who's there?

102
00:04:26,130 --> 00:04:27,060
General Weibei.

103
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:28,460
What are you looking at?

104
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:29,930
Haven't you seen people having an affair?

105
00:04:29,930 --> 00:04:32,360
Keep looking and I'll gouge your eyes out.

106
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,159
Master, bad news!

107
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:37,630
Is this the idea you came up with?

108
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,530
To make it convincing,

109
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:39,960
you need to kiss me hard

110
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,020
and leave hickeys.

111
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,430
Then they'll believe it.

112
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:52,100
General Weibei claims he's presenting gifts by imperial decree,

113
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,960
yet he's having an affair with a maid in my mansion.

114
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:57,520
He's clearly using this to humiliate me,

115
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,760
but actually humiliating Your Majesty.

116
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,700
You're the Grand Tutor.

117
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,130
You've read so many books.

118
00:05:02,130 --> 00:05:02,730
When complaining,

119
00:05:02,730 --> 00:05:03,990
why do you use my words?

120
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,100
Is this true?

121
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:05,900
Yes.

122
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,900
But I was also acting on your decree.

123
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,330
When did I issue a decree

124
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:12,360
letting you have an affair with the Grand Tutor's maid?

125
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,400
Your Majesty bestowed the trial-marriage maid upon me.

126
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:16,730
Naturally, I must present her with betrothal gifts today too.

127
00:05:16,730 --> 00:05:17,860
I sent to the Grand Tutor's mansion

128
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,460
countless gold and jewelry as gifts.

129
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:21,330
The betrothal gift for my beloved

130
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,730
is my sincere love.

131
00:05:22,730 --> 00:05:23,630
Shut up.

132
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:25,160
What kind of wild talk is this?

133
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,530
How can you say it in public?

134
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:28,860
I know you're vulgar, but this is too much.

135
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,100
Grand Tutor.

136
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:34,560
General Weibei was indeed out of line today.

137
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,200
But it's excusable.

138
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,200
I did give him the maid.

139
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,800
For my sake,

140
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,930
please forgive him.

141
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,360
Shut up.

142
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,700
Your Majesty's word is law.

143
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:47,830
It's only right that my family suffers some grievances.

144
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,090
Thank you for your compassion, Your Majesty.

145
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,760
However.

146
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:55,760
This maid's identity is special.

147
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:59,300
She is the daughter of the guilty minister Shen Zhengran.

148
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:00,660
Oh.

149
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:03,730
It turns out to be the eldest daughter of Minister Shen.

150
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:05,700
Your servant, Shen Lvyi, greets Your Majesty.

151
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,200
Thank Your Majesty for sparing my life.

152
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:07,930
Long live Your Majesty!

153
00:06:07,930 --> 00:06:09,000
Long live!

154
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,130
Truly a noble lady.

155
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:12,960
Her etiquette is impeccable.

156
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,630
And she is indeed very beautiful.

157
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:17,760
No wonder she has enchanted my General of Weibei so much.

158
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,560
Lvyi just now

159
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:22,360
failed to find what she was looking for in the Grand Tutor's mansion.

160
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,330
Now she must be hoping to delay the situation.

161
00:06:25,530 --> 00:06:27,530
But His Majesty despises Minister Shen.

162
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:29,300
I need to find a way to cause trouble

163
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,500
and distract His Majesty.
